+
+<p>To access deep telegram bots you just need to click on settings-&gt;switch backend.</p>
+
+<p>Also do check out the <a href="https://pwrtelegram.xyz">PWRTelegram bot API: a boosted version of telegram's bot API that can upload/download files up to 1.5 GB, supports anonymous downloads and much more!</a>.  </p>
 
